snippet.textDisplay:
My interpretation from the song :

The song revolves around the concept of pursuing one's (one soul, two body)❤ dream despite facing obstacles. The music video showcases a girl and a boy expressing their dreams and their difficulties in chasing them.

The boy is encouraging the girl to follow her heart and pursue their dreams. Despite the girl's desire to live her dream, she is fearful of the consequences and societal judgment. In contrast, the boy is providing the encouragement and inviting her to accompany him and to break through all fences and boundaries.

"Once our dream comes true, it will become known to all. The era of Romeo and Juliet's love story has passed; it is now our turn to write our own story."  🥹🫠🥰

In summary, life is short, so embrace it fully. Pursue your dreams and go after them relentlessly. While difficulties may arise, you have the power to overcome them by heeding the wisdom of your heart. 🤗

Beautiful song with perfect blend of depth in its lyrics. Grateful to @cokestudio for sharing yet another masterpiece with us. 🙏
